&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We don&#39;t have an immediate opening for this role right now, but we&#39;re building our candidate pool ahead of anticipated hiring needs this fall into next year. By applying, you&#39;ll be added to our talent community so we can reach out as soon as a position opens.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for an Admissions Enrollment Advisor I to serve as the very first connection for prospective students exploring a nursing career. This isn&#39;t a call-center job, it&#39;s a relationship-building role at the front door of our institution. You&#39;ll guide applicants through every step of the Discover, Commit, Start Application journey, making sure they feel supported, informed, and genuinely seen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time, remote, hourly-nonexempt position with occasional travel (a few times per year) and hours that flex with your assigned time zone, including occasional Saturdays.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Initiate outbound phone calls and handle inbound calls in response to inquiries each day to set appointments and conduct interviews with prospective learners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16448250}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Contact prospective learners to confirm and conduct scheduled appointments, ensuring all necessary information is communicated, any questions are addressed, and adherence to all compliance and accreditation standards is&amp;nbsp;maintained.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16448250}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Provide a daily activity report (DAR) to the Supervisor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16448250}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Generate leads by requesting referrals and enter all new inquiry information in the&amp;nbsp;appropriate system. Follow the contact strategy and track all correspondence with prospective learners in the&amp;nbsp;appropriate system.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16448250}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Utilize the Discover, Commit, Start&amp;nbsp;Application process with prospective learners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16448250}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Assist&amp;nbsp;prospective learners, learner families, and other relevant parties who may be involved in decision-making.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16448250}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Invite qualified applicants to apply, ensuring they receive all necessary information and support throughout the application process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134

