pan class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW263573952 BCX0&quot;&gt; Professor, Didactic will show evidence of participation in academic or professional association related to domain and will &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW263573952 BCX0&quot;&gt;assist&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW263573952 BCX0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW263573952 BCX0&quot;&gt;selection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW263573952 BCX0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and development of faculty. This role may&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW263573952 BCX0&quot;&gt;be responsible for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW263573952 BCX0&quot;&gt; the development and modification of the curriculum in coordination with committees.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role and Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;10&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Monitors, engages, and maintains open communication with learners in all aspects of the nursing education process, including attendance, performance, comprehension, and eval

&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Nightingale College&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nightingale College is a distance education nursing school with a singular purpose: expanding access to quality nursing education and, through it, transforming healthcare. We don&#39;t just train nurses — we build a high-impact community of learners, educators, and collaborators who are committed to changing lives. If you&#39;re driven by mission and energized by meaningful work, you belong here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NCLEX success isn&#39;t just a milestone — it&#39;s the gateway to every learner&#39;s future as a nurse. As an &lt;strong&gt;Assistant Professor I, NCLEX&lt;/strong&gt;, you&#39;ll be the coach, strategist, and champion who helps Nightingale learners and graduates cross that threshold.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this fully remote role, you&#39;ll work directly with PN, ASN, and BSN learners and graduates to identify knowledge gaps, build personalized learning plans, and guide them through every stage of NCLEX preparation. You&#39;ll bring innovative teaching methods, data-informed coaching, and genuine care for learner success to everything you do — all in service of Nightingale&#39;s mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and prepare assigned learners to achieve NCLEX success through meaningful interactions, consistent communication, and customized learning plans — with a focus on those identified as at-risk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor learner progress and maintain open communication throughout the coaching process, including grading and attendance tracking for assigned activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, outline, and facilitate scheduled study sessions and 1:1 coaching appointments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete initial and final evaluations for assigned learners and graduates, and make recommendations for transcript clearance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend NCLEX faculty meetings, participate in committees, and contribute to shared decision-making and faculty activities as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in the implementation of functional projects as they arise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain certification records as required by accreditation, facility, or state board of nursing standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MSN required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability and commitment to serve across all three academic semesters each calendar year&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Doctorate preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience facilitating concept-based nursing education&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in at least one learning management system (LMS) — Canvas preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Microsoft Office (Outlook, Word, Excel, Teams) and other technology platforms used in online nursing education delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Nightingale&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This isn&#39;t a role where you show up and clock out. It&#39;s a role where you show up and change someone&#39;s life. Our collaborators are people who believe in the power of education to create opportunity — and who want to be part of a community that holds that belief in common. We lead with purpose, operate with transparency, and grow together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nightingale College is an equal opportunity employer.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Budgeted Hiring Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$80,000&lt

