s of the&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW212466010 BCX0&quot; data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW212466010 BCX0&quot; data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;College’s mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
