&lt;h3&gt;**Start Date: September 8, 2026**&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nightingale is looking for an experienced &lt;strong&gt;Business Analyst III&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Operational Effectiveness function within Mission Support. This is a senior individual contributor role for someone who thrives on turning ambiguity into clarity — leading requirements definition and workflow documentation for complex, high-impact initiatives with minimal oversight.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll operate as a subject matter expert across the organization: mentoring junior analysts, driving cross-functional alignment, and bridging the gap between operational complexity and solution readiness. If you love untangling messy problems and building the structure that helps big initiatives actually land, this role is built for you.&lt;/p&gt;
