&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end translation of business needs into user stories, functional requirements, and acceptance criteria&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive scope definition, dependency mapping, and success metric development alongside operations leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Independently analyze complex datasets to surface insights, risks, and strategic recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead design of enterprise-level dashboards, reports, and KPIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Workflow Documentation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
