&lt;li&gt;Establish and maintain documentation standards and templates for the BA practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Alignment &amp;amp; Facilitation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
