&lt;li&gt;Drive readiness criteria definition and validation across multiple concurrent initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project &amp;amp; Solution Readiness&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
